                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17800628-4-defend121 t17800628-4-punish21"></join>
               Death
            </rs>.)</p>
               <p>(He was humbly recommended by the Jury to his majesty's mercy.)</p>
               <p>Tried by the First Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice NARES.</p>
